  "name": "RPlog_Hutt_Palace_Raid",
  "title": "Storming Grubba's Palace on Nar Shaddaa",
  "summary": "After a brutal campaign across Nar Shaddaa, the aspiring crimelord Thanos leads his ragtag band of usurpers in a final assault on Grubba the Hutt's palace, backed by the Sith Lord Darth Malign (Tyler) and his agents. The mercenary slicer Kaitlin breaches the door, triggering a smoke-and-flash-grenade firefight against Gamorrean guards, while fighters like Dareus, Sarray, Juran, the sniper Lon Cotar, the merc Axel Vichten, and the reluctant pilot Siren fight inward; the Hutt's slave Raven fires down on the attackers from above. Reaching the throne room, Thanos rejects Grubba's parley and opens fire, but his impulsiveness leaves the group fighting a wall of hardened Hutt mercenaries who refuse quarter. Thanos chases the fleeing Hutt into the hangar just before a massive explosion seals it off, and Malign declares the battle won, ordering a retreat as Axel's bombers prepare to level the palace. In the aftermath Malign slaughters the surviving thugs and abducts a prisoner, Gillian, to serve the Sith, while the wounded Siren and Lon flee with the freed slave Raven, who chooses selfless aid and her own freedom over Grubba's lost cause.",
